Responsibilities:

  Develop and produce marketing collaterals e.g. create infographics or videos to support agency's communications efforts
  Support the execution, monitoring and coordination of campaign assets and roll-out with third-party vendors, and report on campaigns
  Coordinate marketing activities and collate information from external and internal stakeholder for reporting
  Assist in social media listening and media monitoring for compilation into the Daily News Brief as needed
  Any other support required for the smooth running and execution of the department's communications and stakeholder engagement work

Other Information:

  The duration of the traineeship is 6 months
